look like ants?

00:06:23.950 --> 00:06:25.940 align:middle line:90%
There's no suggestion of that.

00:06:25.940 --> 00:06:30.400 align:middle line:84%
In fact, in descriptions or
depictions of them in rock art,

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:33.580 align:middle line:84%
