like Egyptian high priests.

00:06:33.580 --> 00:06:37.030 align:middle line:84%
And you ask, well, who could
these high priests possibly be?

00:06:37.030 --> 00:06:39.880 align:middle line:84%
Could they-- might possibly
have been the Atlanteans,

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:42.730 align:middle line:84%
the survivors that are
teaching the Hopi how

00:06:42.730 --> 00:06:48.190 align:middle line:84%
to enter into a period of stasis
