00:07:26.110 --> 00:07:29.260 align:middle line:84%
Now, if we go from
the thought that

00:07:29.260 --> 00:07:32.920 align:middle line:84%
behind many of these
myths of gigantic floods

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:41.110 align:middle line:84%
are very real events, then what
is the potential real reality

00:07:41.110 --> 00:07:45.490 align:middle line:84%
behind the stories
of the gods that all

00:07:45.490 --> 00:07:47.200 align:middle line:90%
of these ancient cultures have?

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:50.260 align:middle line:84%
Now, what happens there
