00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:51.850 align:middle line:90%
want to go to aliens.

00:07:51.850 --> 00:07:54.400 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not dismissing
the idea of aliens.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.020 align:middle line:84%
But instead of immediately
jumping to aliens,

00:07:57.020 --> 00:08:00.950 align:middle line:84%
let us consider the possibility
that you might have had,

00:08:00.950 --> 00:08:04.317 align:middle line:84%
in ancient times, cultures
existing side by side

00:08:04.317 --> 00:08:05.900 align:middle line:84%
that were, on the
one hand, primitive,

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:09.860 align:middle line:84%
