00:08:20.810 --> 00:08:23.370 align:middle line:84%
Hey, there's going to
be something coming.

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:25.610 align:middle line:84%
There's going to be
a gigantic flood.

00:08:25.610 --> 00:08:28.040 align:middle line:84%
