00:09:52.130 --> 00:09:55.790 align:middle line:10%
It drives the climate
into a warming period.

00:09:55.790 --> 00:09:59.240 align:middle line:10%
Because when you have
this major solar outburst

00:09:59.240 --> 00:10:02.450 align:middle line:10%
at the end of the last Ice
