down, melt ice when it hits it.

00:10:10.680 --> 00:10:15.810 align:middle line:84%
You have incredible flooding
on the surface of the Earth.

00:10:15.810 --> 00:10:19.440 align:middle line:84%
You have increased
earthquake activity.

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:22.200 align:middle line:84%
You have increased
volcanic activity.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:25.380 align:middle line:90%
You have a rising sea levels.

00:10:25.380 --> 00:10:28.270 align:middle line:84%
It would cause, in
some cases, wildfires.

00:10:28.270 --> 00:10:30.310 align:middle line:84%
Then there's
another twist to it,

00:10:30.310 --> 00:10:34.080 align:middle line:84%
