diametrically opposed,

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:05.760 align:middle line:10%
where evidence for
some kind of impactor,

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:10.920 align:middle line:10%
evidence for a solar
outburst, they overlap.

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:16.530 align:middle line:10%
Still, I am 100% convinced that
all of the evidence looking

00:11:16.530 --> 00:11:22.680 align:middle line:10%
